  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 6th level, you aren't afraid to gain a little money, even at the expense of others. When you would deal damage to a creature with a ninjutsu, you may select 1 creature to siphon money from. You gain ryō equal to half the damage the creature received rounding up to the nearest ten. <em><strong>Refined Ninjutsu</strong></em> instead siphon the full amount.</p><p>You may use this feature a number of times equal to your Intelligence Modifier per long rest.</p>",
